{"tid":1805823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"注意！又黎過！山埃毒氣於油麻地再測出超出安全數字上限！","createTime":"2020-01-01T00:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T14:36:10.000Z","uid":1806,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"da2cc804160cf8ae4a53d66f0191e5b071a8b261","tid":1805823,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nzeNkmaMb9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnzeNkmaMb9I&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fd34204f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nzeNkmaMb9I</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rcS6Ze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rcS6Ze.jpg&h=e50701f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0115 #油麻地 #彌敦道 催淚彈<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>山埃毒氣含量12.4ppm</ins></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：測量機係有一個小數點，所以唔好睇咗124ppm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">國際Standard</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>NIOSH: 4.7 PPM<br />\nOccupational exposure limit TLV: 10 ppm as TWA (ACGIH 2001)<br />\nIDLH (Immediate danger)：50 ppm</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">提提大家今日1月1日維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">HKGETV Social Media Platform</span></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3f66b17b\" data-auto-link target=\"